{
  "text": "Excessive production of reactive oxygen species causes testicular damage, which can be reverted by administration of antioxidants [CITATION_1] . Antioxidants have also been demonstrated to enhance testicular function and sperm count in rats [CITATION_2] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "41301435",
    "[CITATION_2]": "73270270"
